---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  structuredDataType="WebPage"
  structuredData={{
    "@type": "Article",
    "headline": "Ultimate Web Design Guide 2025",
    "author": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    },
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Beach Bird Studios"
    }
  }}
>
  <Header />
  
  <Hero 
    headline="The Ultimate <span class='text-yellow-400'>Web Design</span> Guide for 2025"
    subheadline="Everything you need to know about modern web design - from planning to launch and beyond"
    primaryCTA={{
      text: "Get Your Free Consultation",
      href: "/contact"
    }}
    secondaryCTA={{
      text: "View Our Work",
      href: "/about"
    }}
  />

  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Web design in 2025 is more complex and more important than ever. With over 60% of web traffic coming from mobile devices, 
          Google's emphasis on Core Web Vitals, and users expecting instant, seamless experiences, getting your website right 
          is critical for business success.
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-8">
          This comprehensive guide covers everything you need to know about modern web design - whether you're planning your first 
          website, considering a redesign, or just want to understand what makes websites successful in today's digital landscape.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <i data-lucide="info" class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-3">
              <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
                <strong>Quick Tip:</strong> The average website visitor decides whether to stay or leave within 15 seconds. 
                Every design decision should be made with this in mind.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">More Helpful Resources</h3>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div>
              <a href="/small-business-seo-guide" class="block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border hover:border-green-300 transition-colors">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Small Business SEO Guide</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Learn how to get found in local search results</p>
              </a>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a href="/website-cost-guide" class="block p-4 bg-white rounded-lg border hover:border-green-300 transition-colors">
                <h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-2">Website Cost Guide</h4>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Understand website pricing and get better value</p>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Design Principles -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6 Core Principles of Modern Web Design</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          These fundamental principles guide every successful web design project. Master these, and you're well on your way to a website that works.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={designPrinciples} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Design Process Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">The Professional Web Design Process</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Understanding the process helps you work better with designers and know what to expect.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 font-bold text-lg">1</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Discovery & Strategy</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Understanding your business goals, target audience, and competitive landscape. This phase includes brand analysis, 
              user research, and technical requirements gathering. The foundation of every successful project.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Strategy document, user personas, competitive analysis, technical specification</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-green-100 text-green-600 font-bold text-lg">2</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Information Architecture & Wireframes</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Organizing content and planning user flows before visual design begins. This ensures logical navigation 
              and that important information is easy to find. Structure first, beauty second.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Site map, user flow diagrams, wireframes for key pages</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-600 font-bold text-lg">3</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Visual Design</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Creating the visual identity, color schemes, typography, and overall aesthetic that reflects your brand 
              and appeals to your target audience. This is where your website starts to come alive.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Design mockups, style guide, asset library, responsive designs</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-purple-100 text-purple-600 font-bold text-lg">4</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Development & Testing</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Converting designs into working code, integrating content management systems, and ensuring everything 
              works perfectly across all devices and browsers. Quality assurance is critical.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Functional website, CMS setup, performance optimization, cross-browser testing</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-6">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-600 font-bold text-lg">5</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Launch & Optimization</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Going live, setting up analytics, monitoring performance, and making improvements based on real user data. 
              Launch is just the beginning - ongoing optimization is where real results happen.
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600"><strong>Deliverables:</strong> Live website, analytics setup, performance monitoring, optimization plan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modern Design Trends -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2025 Web Design Trends That Actually Matter</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Not all trends are worth following. These design approaches improve user experience and business results.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={modernTrends} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Common Mistakes -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6 Costly Web Design Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Learn from common pitfalls that hurt user experience and business growth. Prevention is better than fixing later.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={commonMistakes} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Choosing a Designer -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">How to Choose the Right Web Designer</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          The designer you choose can make or break your project. Here's what to look for.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <FeatureGrid features={choosingDesigner} />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Investment & ROI Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Understanding Web Design Investment</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Quality web design is an investment in your business growth, not just an expense.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-8 mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">What Affects Web Design Pricing?</h3>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Project Scope Factors:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Number of pages and features</li>
              <li>• Custom functionality requirements</li>
              <li>• Content creation needs</li>
              <li>• Integration with existing systems</li>
              <li>• E-commerce capabilities</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Quality Factors:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
              <li>• Designer experience and skill level</li>
              <li>• Custom vs template-based design</li>
              <li>• Performance optimization</li>
              <li>• SEO implementation</li>
              <li>• Ongoing support included</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Measuring Your Website's ROI</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          A well-designed website pays for itself through increased leads, sales, and credibility. Track these metrics:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">25%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Average increase in conversion rate with professional design</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">40%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">More time spent on site with good UX design</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">60%</div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Higher credibility perception with professional design</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Checklist Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-cream-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Web Design Project Checklist</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
          Use this checklist to ensure your web design project covers all the essentials.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Before You Start</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Define your primary business goals</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Identify your target audience</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Research competitors' websites</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Gather brand assets and content</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Set a realistic budget range</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">During Development</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Test on multiple devices</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Optimize for page speed</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Implement SEO basics</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Set up analytics tracking</span>
              </label>
              <label class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                <input type="checkbox" class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600">
                <span class="text-gray-700">Plan for ongoing maintenance</span>
              </label>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Next Steps CTA -->
  <CTASection 
    headline="Ready to Start Your Web Design Project?"
    description="Let's discuss your goals and create a website that drives real business results. Free consultation with no obligation."
    primaryCTA={{
      text: "Get Your Free Consultation",
      href: "/contact"
    }}
    secondaryCTA={{
      text: "View Our Portfolio",
      href: "/about"
    }}
  />

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose {
    color: #374151;
  }
  
  .form-checkbox:checked {
    background-color: #3B82F6;
    border-color: #3B82F6;
  }
  
  .bg-cream-50 {
    background-color: rgba(245, 230, 211, 0.3);
  }
</style>